OL,3,CTeenager's shock as woman and child
OL,4,Crun through level crossing
OL,6,FWatch as a woman with a child rushes
OL,7,Facross train tracks as barriers are
OL,8,Flowering. Credit: Brandon Roberts
OL,10,FA teenager has told ITV News Central
OL,11,Fhe watched in shock as he filmed a
OL,12,Fwoman pull a crying child across a
OL,13,Flevel crossing as the barriers came
OL,14,Fdown.
OL,16,FThe footage, labelled as "deeply
OL,17,Fconcerning" by Network Rail, shows the
OL,18,Fpair and a man rushing across railway
OL,19,Ftracks as the bell rings to warn of an
OL,20,Fincoming train.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
