OL,3,CTeenager's shock as woman and child
OL,4,Crun through level crossing
OL,6,FThe woman appears to have to pull the
OL,7,Fchild through the first set of
OL,8,Fbarriers. She then has to duck under
OL,9,Fthe second set of lowering barriers.
OL,11,FTwo minutes later, a train goes past.
OL,13,FThe video, shared on social media by
OL,14,F16-year-old Brandon Roberts, was
OL,15,Ffilmed at Tutbury and Hatton Station,
OL,16,Fon the Derbyshire-Staffordshire border
OL,17,Fon Saturday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
