OL,3,CTeenager's shock as woman and child
OL,4,Crun through level crossing
OL,6,FBrandon, who is a fan of level
OL,7,Fcrossings and trains, said: "I've seen
OL,8,Fa few misuse incidents while filming
OL,9,Flevel crossings but never with a child!
OL,11,F"It was quite shocking to be honest
OL,12,Fbecause that child was probably
OL,13,Fterrified."
OL,15,FHe continued: "Luckily the signaller
OL,16,Fwas watching over the crossing to stop
OL,17,Fthe barriers.
OL,19,F"All he could do was stop the barriers
OL,20,Fthen continue lowering them once it
OL,21,Fwas clear.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
