OL,3,CTeenager's shock as woman and child
OL,4,Crun through level crossing
OL,6,FThe teenager from Wrexham said he
OL,7,Ftravelled to the area because it is
OL,8,Fone of the small amount of crossings
OL,9,Fthat still have bells instead of
OL,10,Falarms.
OL,12,FA Network Rail spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"This kind of behaviour is deeply
OL,14,Fconcerning and could have had tragic
OL,15,Fconsequences.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
