PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777903640
OL,3,CTeenager's shock as woman and child
OL,4,Crun through level crossing
OL,6,F"Level crossing barriers and warning
OL,7,Flights are there for good reason.
OL,8,FIgnoring them not only endangers those
OL,9,Ftaking this action, but also puts
OL,10,Ftrain passengers, railway staff and
OL,11,Fother members of the public at risk
OL,12,Ftoo.
OL,14,F"One poor decision can change lives
OL,15,Fforever."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@IO]
